# ⚡ TaskFlow Pro

![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-success)
![PHP](https://img.shields.io/badge/PHP-8.x-blue)
![MySQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/MySQL-database-orange)
![UI](https://img.shields.io/badge/UI-modern-purple)

A clean, multi-user task management web app built with PHP & MySQL, focused on simplicity, performance, and smooth user experience.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 *Coming Soon*: **[Deploy Link Here](#)**

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔐 Authentication (Login / Register)
* 👥 Multi-user task isolation
* ➕ Add / ✔ Complete / ❌ Delete tasks
* 🎯 Priority tagging
* 🔍 Instant search
* ⏱️ Pomodoro timer
* 📊 Analytics dashboard

---

## 🧠 Highlights

* Session-based secure auth
* Clean and responsive UI
* Smooth interactions & micro-animations
* Lightweight and fast

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

**PHP • MySQL • JavaScript • CSS**

---

## 🌱 Future Scope

* 🔔 Notifications
* 📅 Calendar integration
* 🎯 Drag & drop tasks

